ority of any way but the German way.\u003cbr /\u003e How many global errors of these types are being made today by world military leaders, and what will be the consequences?\u003cbr /\u003e \u003cbr /\u003e I was six years old when this book first came out and I remember it causing quite a stir amount my parents' friends as they passed their one copy from couple to couple.\u003cbr /\u003e I spoke to my mother about it this weekend, and she said her reaction to it was shock. \u003cbr /\u003e She and I agree that all we were taught about WWI was that Kaiser Wilhelm got too big for his britches, some minor Prince got shot by a nutcase and Germany used it as an excuse to invade France. England magnanimously came to France's rescue. Not. what. happened. \u003cbr /\u003e \u003cbr /\u003eDo read this, even if you have to draw the battle plans out on graph paper like I did to understand parts of it. So much of our 21st century world makes sense when you understand the beginning of the last century.","rating":5,"shelving":{"__typename":"Shelving","shelf":{"__typename":"Shelf","name":"read","webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/review/list/58567012?shelf=read"},"taggings":[],"webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2532019425"},"likeCount":44,"viewerHasLiked":null,"commentCount":5,"viewerCanComment({\"resourceType\":\"review\"})":null},"Work:kca://work/amzn1.gr.work.v1.61UNdfN7q3K9LbZfkpX4wA":{"id":"kca://work/amzn1.gr.work.v1.61UNdfN7q3K9LbZfkpX4wA","__typename":"Work","legacyId":1884932,"bestBook":{"__ref":"Book:kca://book/amzn1.gr.book.v1.sg3l_p7nPjafDnYfrmS1ew"},"details":{"__typename":"WorkDetails","webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/work/1884932-the-guns-of-august","shelvesUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/work/shelves/1884932-the-guns-of-august","publicationTime":-252432000000,"originalTitle":"The Guns of August","awardsWon":[{"__typename":"Award","name":"Pulitzer Prize","webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/award/show/16-pulitzer-prize","awardedAt":-220896000000,"cat